The crucible is a [Basic Machine](https://github.com/Slimefun/Slimefun4/wiki/Basic-Machines) used to create liquids out of different items and blocks.

## Obtaining a Crucible
Using the [Enhanced Crafting Table](https://github.com/Slimefun/Slimefun4/wiki/Enhanced-Crafting-Table) with 6 terracotta and a flint and steel the crucible can be crafted.
After this the crucible can be placed and used.

## Lava Items
* 16 Cobblestone
* 16 Netherrack
* 12 Stone
* 1 Obsidian
* 12 Terracotta
* 12 of any Colored Terracotta
* 8 Blackstone
* 12 Basalt
## Water Items
* 16 Leaves of any Kind
